      <odd id="aspace_ca57637f61a933f7509fd9d11d438856">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 21-A (YRG 21-A), Central records and records of the dean of the Yale Divinity School.</p>  
      </odd>
