      <scopecontent id="aspace_336e6c0594bdc90a1c3aec6448c3b4e8">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of reports, minutes, lists, correspondence, subject files, daybooks, alumni records, student prize materials, and student data documenting the administrative operations of the Yale Divinity School.</p>  
